{"title":"Hexo更换Aurora主题","uid":"339ccb0884c7b3b46e5f86760d5c896a","slug":"Hexo更换Aurora主题","date":"2023-01-08T12:01:19.000Z","updated":"2023-01-09T08:58:44.941Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo更换Aurora主题.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/mdimg/banner/1.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"更换主题\"><a href=\"#更换主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更换主题\"></a>更换主题</h2><p>原先使用的<a href=\"https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery\">matery</a>主题是跟教程从头到尾设置的，在学会搭建博客后便先更换一个心仪的主题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"过程中遇到的问题\"><a href=\"#过程中遇到的问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"过程中遇到的问题\"></a>过程中遇到的问题</h2><h3 id=\"使用git推送报错\"><a href=\"#使用git推送报错\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用git推送报错\"></a>使用git推送报错</h3><ul>\n<li><p>移动过git安装目录，需重新设置注册表</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>win + R 运行 cmd</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>输入 regedit 打开注册表</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>依次寻找以下目录：</p>\n<p>HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Classes\\Directory\\shell</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改 git_shell 和 git_gui 的目录及其内部 command 的目录，改为当前git的安装目录</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>再依次寻找以下目录：</p>\n<p>HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Classes\\Directory\\background\\shell</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改 git_shell 和 git_gui 同上</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>最后打开 git bush 配置 ca-bundle.crt 目录</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ git config --system http.sslcainfo &quot;自己的git目录\\mingw64\\ssl\\certs\\ca-bundle.crt&quot;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"在原先Hexo根目录中安装Aurora主题上传后没有成功\"><a href=\"#在原先Hexo根目录中安装Aurora主题上传后没有成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在原先Hexo根目录中安装Aurora主题上传后没有成功\"></a>在原先Hexo根目录中安装Aurora主题上传后没有成功</h3><ul>\n<li><p>一开始我以为是本地文件被我改乱了，于是我重新创建了一个文件夹进行重新部署，但并未解决</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>最后发现是clone命令执行失败，便去GitHub仓库手动下载，将下载的文件解压至themes目录下，在<code>_config.yml</code>中设置theme为aurora，如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">theme: aurora</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用hexo-g报错\"><a href=\"#使用hexo-g报错\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用hexo g报错\"></a>使用hexo g报错</h3><ul>\n<li><p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230108204643157.png\" alt=\"image-20230108204643157\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>报错原因是 “:” 后面没有加上空格</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>检查<code>_config.yml</code>和<code>_config.aurora.yml</code>，未发现异常</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>再检查”_post“下的md文件，最终发现是tags后没加空格，如图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230108205059634.png\" alt=\"image-20230108205059634\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"配置-valine-评论插件\"><a href=\"#配置-valine-评论插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 valine 评论插件\"></a>配置 valine 评论插件</h3><ul>\n<li><p>注册 <a href=\"https://www.leancloud.cn/\">LeanCloud</a> 账号，进入控制台</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>点击创建应用</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230109161406035.png\" alt=\"image-20230109161406035\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>应用名称随便写，选择开发版</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230109161505229.png\" alt=\"image-20230109161505229\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建完毕后，点击设置</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230109161552919.png\" alt=\"image-20230109161552919\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>进入应用凭证，获取<code>AppID</code>和<code>AppKey</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230109161845120.png\" alt=\"image-20230109161845120\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在<code>_config.aurora.yml</code>中设置完成</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"配置-Gitalk【失败】\"><a href=\"#配置-Gitalk【失败】\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 Gitalk【失败】\"></a>配置 Gitalk【失败】</h3><ul>\n<li><p>在GitHub中新建一个仓库，专门存放评论内容</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开仓库设置：</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230108210640222.png\" alt=\"image-20230108210640222\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>往下一翻就能看到Issues，默认是打开的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230108210844424.png\" alt=\"image-20230108210844424\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>注册一个 Github Application，具体步骤如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230108211134295.png\" alt=\"image-20230108211134295\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>注册完成后即可获取 Client ID 和 Client Secret(需要手动生成)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置 proxy，默认值为：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">proxy: &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com&#x2F;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;login&#x2F;oauth&#x2F;access_token&#39;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"自定义页面右侧资料卡片不显示信息\"><a href=\"#自定义页面右侧资料卡片不显示信息\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义页面右侧资料卡片不显示信息\"></a>自定义页面右侧资料卡片不显示信息</h3><ul>\n<li><p>使用<code>F12</code>打开”网络“标签，发现<code>blog-author.json</code>报404</p>\n<p><img src=\"../img/mdimg/image-20230109165352840.png\" alt=\"image-20230109165352840\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>根据URL找到该文件夹下，发现没有生成<code>blog-author.json</code>文件，初步判断是生成页面的代码除了问题，但未找到并解决</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>于是手动复制生成的<code>WIce.json</code>并更名为<code>blog-author.json</code>，运行后发现已解决</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"更换主题原先使用的matery主题是跟教程从头到尾设置的，在学会搭建博客后便先更换一个心仪的主题。 过程中遇到的问题使用git推送报错 移动过git安装目录，需重新设置注册表 win + R 运行 cmd 输入 regedit 打开注册表 依次寻找以下目录： HKEY_LOCAL...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":1,"path":"api/categories/blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"theme","slug":"theme","count":1,"path":"api/tags/theme.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">更换主题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">过程中遇到的问题</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8git%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用git推送报错</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9C%A8%E5%8E%9F%E5%85%88Hexo%E6%A0%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Aurora%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E5%90%8E%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">在原先Hexo根目录中安装Aurora主题上传后没有成功</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo-g%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用hexo g报错</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-valine-%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">配置 valine 评论插件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-Gitalk%E3%80%90%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E3%80%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">配置 Gitalk【失败】</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">自定义页面右侧资料卡片不显示信息</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"WIce","slug":"wice","avatar":"/img/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"「如果你想攀登高峰，切莫把彩虹当作梯子。」","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/BILIBILI_LOGO.svg","link":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1g4411D7LC/?share_source=copy_web&vd_source=fe444415f88308f70a8c17b15686af37"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"我的第一个博客","uid":"e14eef3688a1f85d86f16a179a81ffa4","slug":"我的第一个博客","date":"2023-01-08T11:57:19.000Z","updated":"2023-01-08T13:23:55.567Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/我的第一个博客.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/mdimg/banner/mqm.jpg","text":"欢迎来到WIce的窝！ 我的第一个博客心路历程o(￣▽￣)ｄ 这是我的第一个博客，经过一下午的捣鼓，终于通过Hexo&amp;GitHub的方式把它做了出来。 在很早之前我就萌生了搭建一个属于自己的博客的想法，在网上看了许多教程，大多数都是通过购买云服务器搭建的，但是碍于难以言喻...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":694,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":1,"path":"api/tags/blog.json"}],"author":{"name":"WIce","slug":"wice","avatar":"/img/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"「如果你想攀登高峰，切莫把彩虹当作梯子。」","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":